#: pb/web/offline.php:20
msgid ""
"Have you ever noticed that you never bump into your neighbours online?\n"
"This means that most websites can't offer much help to people trying\n"
"to do things on their street or in their local community."
msgstr ""
"Ydych chi wedi sylwi eich bod chi byth yn cwrdd &acirc;'ch cymdogion arlein?\n"
"Mae hyn yn golygu nad yw'r rhan fwya o wefannau yn gallu bod o gymorth i'r\n"
"rhai sy'n ceisio gwneud pethau ar eu stryd, pentref, neu gymuned leol."

#: pb/web/offline.php:23
msgid ""
"PledgeBank is different. We've designed PledgeBank to make it easy to\n"
"get word of your pledges to your neighbours, and easy for them to get\n"
"involved even if they never use the internet."
msgstr ""
"Mae PledgeBank yn wahanol. Rydym wedi cynllunio PledgeBank i hwyluso lledu'r\n"
"gair am eich addewidion i'ch cymdogion, ac yn hawdd iddyn nhw gymryd rhan\n"
"hyd yn oed os dydyn nhw byth yn defnyddio'r rhyngrwyd."

