#: pb/web/offline.php:33
msgid ""
"Every pledge created on PledgeBank comes with a set of automatically\n"
"generated flyers."
msgstr ""
"Daw pob addewid PledgeBank &acirc; set o daflenni sy'n cael\n"
"eu creu yn awtomatig."

#: pb/web/offline.php:35
msgid ""
"These flyers tell people what your pledge is and how to sign up.\n"
"They're ideal for posting through doors, pinning on notice-boards,\n"
"handing out at school gates - whatever you want. If you've created a\n"
"pledge yourself, you can ask your signers to print and distribute\n"
"leaflets themselves, spreading the word further."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r taflenni hyn yn dweud wrth pawb beth yw eich addewid a sut\n"
"i'w lofnodi. Maent yn ddelfrydol ar gyfer postio trwy ddrysau, rhoi ar\n"
"negesfyrddau, dosbarthu wrth i&ecirc;t yr ysgol - beth bynnag a fynnoch chi.\n"
"Os taw chi sy wedi creu'r addewid, gallwch ofyn i'r rhai sy'n ei lofnodi i'ch\n"
"helpu lledu'r gair gan argraffu a dosbarthu'r taflenni eu hunain."

#: pb/web/offline.php:40
msgid ""
"Each flyer tells people how to sign up either via the web, or via a\n"
"simple two word text message."
msgstr "Mae pob taflen yn esbonio sut i lofnodi'r addewid, naill ai trwy'r we,/nneu gan anfon neges destun dau air."

#: pb/web/offline.php:47
msgid "Mobile Phones"
msgstr "Ffonnau Symudol"

#: pb/web/offline.php:49
msgid ""
"The ability to sign up via text message is powerful because it means\n"
"that people who never use the Internet can sign up, and you can get\n"
"someone to sign up even if they're nowhere near a computer."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r gallu i lofnodi trwy neges destun yn bwerus: gall pobl sy byth yn\n"
"defnyddio'r rhyngrwyd lofnodi'r addewid, a chewch chi lofnodwyr sy ddim\n"
"yn agos at gyfrifiadur."

